text: Yu-Gi-Oh 5Ds is a spin-off series of the original Yu-Gi-Oh franchise. It follows the protagonist Yusei Fudo on adventure, first to get his Stardust dragon back then many other adventures throughout the series. Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D's has many song sets. ==Plot== Yusei Fudo, tests his duel runner and his friend Riley gives him a chip. Meanwhile the world champ Jack easily beats him. Category:Japanese television series
title: Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D's
